Probably writing poetry or exploring the world as a travel blogger.
Biggest pet peeve?
People who are close-minded and unwilling to consider different perspectives.
Do you turn off the light when you leave a room?
Yes, always.
Least favourite film?
I can't think of one off the top of my head, but I generally don't enjoy horror movies.
What do you eat for breakfast?
I usually have a bowl of oatmeal with fruits and nuts.
What did you want to be when you were a child?
I wanted to be an astronaut and explore outer space.
Tea or coffee?
Tea, definitely.
Would you rather have world domination or achieve world peace?
Definitely achieve world peace.
